# Templates Directory

This directory will contain Handlebars templates for Docker Compose generation.
Templates will be created by another agent.

Expected templates:
- docker-compose.hbs - Main Docker Compose template
- docker-compose.saas.hbs - SaaS-specific template
- docker-compose.dedicated.hbs - Dedicated-specific template
- service-*.hbs - Individual service templates
- env.hbs - Environment template
- readme.hbs - Deployment documentation template
